node.title: Search for Wayne Taylor: Body found at base of cliff
node.description: Search teams looking for missing man Wayne Taylor have found a body at the base of a cliff north of Kaik≈çura.
node.content:
["Search teams looking for missing man Wayne Taylor have found a body north of Kaikōura.", "", "
File photo. Photo: Supplied/ Police
", "The 54-year-old was last seen on 20 February in Blenheim and had been expected to drive to Christchurch.", "In a statement, police said Specialist LandSAR teams had found a body matching Taylor's description yesterday afternoon.", "The body was located at the base of a cliff inland from where his car was found at a loookout north of Kaikoura.", "Police said his death was not considered suspicious and would be referred to the coroner."]
